Note: in Desktop mode, press "3" to equip the Protoflux Tool
1.  Open Dashboard and select "Inventory"
2.  "Resonite Essentials"
3.  "Tools"
4.  Double-click the Protoflux Tool to spawn a tool
5.  Select the tool, select "Equip Protoflux Tool"
Note: in Desktop mode, press CTRL+T to open the Context Menu.
6.  Open the Context Menu and select "Browse Nodes"
7.  Select "Users"
8.  Select "Local User"
9.  Double-click to spawn a "Local User" node
10. Delete a node by grabbing it, opening the Context menu, and selecting "Destroy"
